        <updateDate>2022-07-07T21:07:19Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Honoring Civil Servants Killed in the Line of Duty Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases benefits to survivors of federal employees who die in the line of duty.</p> <p>Specifically, the bill increases the death benefit for federal employees from $10,000 to $100,000 and increases the funeral benefit from $800 to $8,800. Both amounts must be adjusted annually for inflation.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
